a. single target mana regen boost<br>
b. can be purchased in Firiona Vie and Overthere<br>
<br>
Chase the Moon<br>
a. single target fear<br>
b. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Disempower<br>
a. single target debuff<br>
Decrease Stamina (10 - 20)<br>
Decrease Strength (14 - 15)<br>
Decrease AC (7 - 9)<br>
b. The most powerful thing about it is that it stacks with the Enfeeblement Series of Spells.<br>
c. This spell will stack with Feckless Might or Insepid Weakness, but not Listless Power.<br>
d. research spell (see Research for components) or can be purchsed in Cabilis, Grobb, Halas, Oggok Shaman Guilds<br>
<br>
Enchant: Electrum<br>
a. single target enchantment<br>
Turns a bar of electrum into enchanted electrum<br>
b. requires a bar of electrum<br>
c. can be purchased in Neriak Library<br>
<br>
Enthrall<br>
a. single target mez<br>
Mesmerise<br>
Reduce Hate<br>
b. any non-damage debuff may be cast upon the target without breaking the mez. These include Tashan, the Weaken Series, or Slow Series.<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Identify<br>
a. Identify will reveal the lore information of an item<br>
b. The target of the spell must be holding the item to be identified in hand, as if he were about to transfer it from one inventory slot to another.<br>
c. can be purchased in enchanter, wizard, mage, necro, sk, and caster guilds<br>
<br>
Illusion: Barbarian<br>
a. self only illusion and buff<br>
Change Form (Barbarian)<br>
Faction Modifier (Barbarian)<br>
New Combat Skill: Slam<br>
b. This spell will reduce your night sight.<br>
c. can be purchased in <br>
Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds Erudin City Library<br>
Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Illusion: Dwarf<br>
a. self only illusion<br>
Change Form (Dwarf)<br>
Faction Modifier (Dwarf)<br>
b. can be purchased in <br>
Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds Erudin City Library<br>
Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Illusion: Tree<br>
a. self only illusion<br>
Change Form (Tree)<br>
Faction Modifier (Tree)<br>
Root<br>
b. you cannot move while in this form.<br>
c. can be purchased in <br>
Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds Erudin City Library<br>
Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Invisibility v Undead<br>
a. single target buff<br>
b. You must be grouped to cast this spell on another person<br>
c. Casting this spell on yourself will release any pets you have, charmed or summoned.<br>
d. does not stack with invisibility<br>
e. it will drop as soon as you cast another spell<br>
f. can be purchased in shaman, cleric, paladin, sk, necro, and caster guilds<br>
<br>
Levitate<br>
a. single target buff<br>
Levitate will allow you to float off the ground for a time<br>
b. Levitate can be refreshed. This means that you do not have to fall to the ground before you recast. <br>
c. you cannot jump while levitating<br>
d. levitate will eliminate damage taken from a &quot;fall.&quot;<br>
e. requires one bat wing per cast<br>
f. research spell (see Research for components) or can be purchased in shaman, druid, and ranger guilds.<br>
<br>
Mesmerisation<br>
a. area effect mez<br>
Stun (36 Seconds)<br>
Reduce Hate<br>
b. a DoT or any damage to the mob will break the spell. Debuffs however will not.<br>
c. This spell can be renewed before the first cast wears off, however individual mesmerise spells such as Dazzle will not stack with it.<br>
d. research only (see Research for components)<br>
<br>
Quickness<br>
a. single target buff<br>
Increase Attack Speed by (28 - 30%)<br>
b. It will stack with haste items, but not with any other haste spell or song.<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Rune I<br>
a. single target shield<br>
Absorb Damage (27 - 55)<br>
b. requires cats eye agate<br>
c. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Sanity Warp<br>
a. single target DD<br>
All or Nothing Direct Damage (88 - 95)<br>
b. can be purchased in Ak`Anon, Felwithe, Freeport, Neriak, Qeynos Casters Guilds, Erudin Palace Ench Guild<br>
<br>
Shalee`s Animation<br>
a. summon pet<br>
b. requires 2 tiny daggers<br>
c. can be purchased in Highhold Keep<br>
<br>
Shielding<br>
a. self only buff<br>
Increase HP (46 - 50)<br>
Increase Magic Resist (12)<br>
Increase AC (12 - 14)<br>
b. It will stack with Cleric or Druid HP buffs, but not the Shaman Talisman spell.<br>
